productDescription: Rose Milk Tres Leches Cake is super moist (Ras Malai Cake) soaked in rich rose-flavored milk and topped with whipped cream. The cake is deliciously light, airy, and fluffy. Can be served as dessert. Available in both variant Egg/Eggless
Saffron Milk Tres Leches Cake is an air-light spongy (Ras Malai Cake) soaked in rich saffron-flavored milk and topped with whipped cream and pistachios. Available in both variant Egg/Eggless

A Chocolate Truffle Cake has dense, moist chocolate cake layers with silky smooth chocolate ganache frosting. With rich chocolate flavor, it is the perfect indulgence. Available in both variant Egg/Eggless

A classic Carrot Layer Cake baked with freshly grated carrot, cinnamon, and walnut, topped with cream cheese frosting. It's light in taste which makes it a perfect tea cake. Available in both variant Egg/Eggless
A decadent cake of moist chocolate layers and creamy chocolate mousse topped with luscious chocolate ganache. Available in both variant Egg/Eggless
A mildly sweet and fluffy vanilla flavor sponge with fresh blueberries and a hint of lemon, layered with cream cheese frosting. Available in both variant Egg/Eggless
A melt-in-mouth chiffon cake layered with fresh fruits and whipped cream. Available in both variant Egg/Eggless
Experience the timeless allure of buttery, caramelized goodness. With homemade butterscotch sauce and chips giving a classic treat to your taste buds. Available in both variant Egg/Eggless
Indulge in the rich and harmonious pairing of decadent chocolate and the citrusy zest of fresh oranges, creating a flavor fusion that's simply irresistible. Available in both variant Egg/Eggless
Immerse yourself in the tropical symphony of ripe mangoes blended with the invigorating essence of passion fruit. Available in both variant Egg/Eggless
